---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Krishna's Knowledge Journal"
  description="Learn about the mission and philosophy behind Krishna's Knowledge Journal."
>

  <Section
    title="About the Journal"
    description="Understanding Finance from First Principles."
  >

    <p>

      Krishna's Knowledge Journal is an independent educational publication
      dedicated to finance, economics, Indian banking, taxation and history.
      Its purpose is to explain complex ideas through first-principles
      thinking, logical reasoning and historical context.

    </p>

    <p>

      Rather than following market trends or short-term opinions,
      the journal focuses on timeless concepts that help readers
      build a deeper and more practical understanding of the subjects
      it covers.

    </p>

    <p>

      Every article is researched and written with the objective of
      being clear, accurate and valuable for years to come.

    </p>

    <p>

      Krishna's Knowledge Journal is written and maintained by{" "}
      <strong>Krishna Pal</strong>, with the belief that genuine
      understanding begins by questioning assumptions and learning
      from first principles.

    </p>

  </Section>

</BaseLayout>